      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "DIRECTOR, FBI (62-83894) AIRTEL AMSD",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "DETROIT FLYING SAUCERS CLUB, ESP-X. ONE [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "[REDACTED] WHO IS A MEMBER OF ABOVE CLUB,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "ADVISED THAT [REDACTED] TWICE HAS",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "STATED HE IS \"WORKING IN CONJUNCTION WITH THE FBI AND HAS BEEN",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "TOLD TO REPORT TO WASHINGTON, D.C. FOR A CONFERENCE.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "REPORTEDLY SAID HE HAS BEEN INSTRUCTED TO BRING ANOTHER CLUB",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "OFFICER, [REDACTED], WITH HIM. [REDACTED] ARE",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "COUSINS. WHEN THE TIME CAME TO GO TO WASHINGTON, [REDACTED] SAID IT",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "WAS IMPOSSIBLE FOR HIM TO GO AND THEY WOULD DO SO LATER. BOTH",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "OF [REDACTED] STATEMENTS WERE MADE WITHIN PAST MONTH. THE DETROIT",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "OFFICE IS PREPARING A REPORT SUITABLE FOR DISSEMINATION ON THIS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "CLUB. IMMEDIATELY AFTER 1/15/55, [REDACTED] WILL BE INTERVIEWED BY",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "DETROIT REGARDING ABOVE STATEMENTS, REPRIMANDED AND CAUTIONED",
